Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:23.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Whatever,0,0,0,,I mean that the depth of your breathing has already surpassed all other Chi You in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう既に 歴代の蚩尤(しゆう)を\Nしのいでるって話だから
